課程概述 Course Description
       •To achieve the basic understanding of the Taiwanese traditional theatrical arts.
•To develop students’ interest in local arts and appreciation to the aesthetic.
•To understand the importance of cultural preservation and innovation.

•To achieve the basic understanding of the Taiwanese traditional theatrical arts.
•To develop students’ interest in local arts and appreciation to the aesthetic.
•To understand the importance of cultural preservation and innovation.
    

課程學習目標 Course Objectives
對於台灣傳統戲曲文化有基本的認識。培養對本土文化的興趣與藝術美感的喜好。瞭解文化保存與創新的重要性。To achieve the basic understanding of the Taiwanese traditional theatrical arts.To develop students’ interest in local arts and appreciation to the aesthetic.To understand the importance of cultural preservation and innovation. 

課程進度 Course Outline


週次 Week進度說明 Progress Description
1課程介紹; 劇場的起源Introduction to the Course and Class Evaluation; the Beginning of Theatre          2中國劇場的起源與功能The Beginning and Functions of Chinese Theatre.3京劇的角色分類與動作The Character Types and Body Movements of Beijing (Peking) Opera.4簡介京劇在台灣的發展與特色The Development and its Characteristics of Beijing (Peking) Opera in Taiwan.5新編京劇賞析Video Appreciation: New Beijing Opera6歌仔戲的起源與初期型態The Origin of Taiwanese Opera and its Early Styles7二戰前後的歌仔戲發展The Development of Taiwanese Opera Before and After WWII8大眾媒體與台灣歌仔戲Taiwanese Opera vs. Mass Media9期中報告Midterm Report10現代歌仔戲賞析Video Appreciation: Modern Taiwanese Opera11布袋戲的起源與初期型態The Origin of Taiwanese Puppetry and its Early Styles12傳統布袋戲賞析Video Appreciation: Traditional Taiwanese Puppetry13大眾媒體與布袋戲Mass Media vs. Taiwanese Puppetry14現代布袋戲特色與發展The Characteristics and Development of Modern Taiwanese Puppetry15當代偶動漫賞析Video Appreciation: Contemporary Taiwanese Puppet Animation16台灣其他偶戲形式Other Taiwanese Puppet Shows17期末報告Final Presentation18期末報告Final Presentation 

